last Thursday.

148
00:07:53,106 --> 00:07:57,942
I show up on what he considers his turf,
and he went ballistic.

149
00:07:58,011 --> 00:07:59,979
Were you trying
to steal his client?

150
00:08:00,046 --> 00:08:01,741
Forget he said that.
He's sorry.

151
00:08:01,815 --> 00:08:03,715
I'm what?
Sorry.

152
00:08:03,783 --> 00:08:04,841
Right, we covered that.

153
00:08:04,918 --> 00:08:09,947
So, you showed up at
Monckton's workplace because...

154
00:08:10,023 --> 00:08:12,458
Well, about 10 days ago,

155
