159
00:08:26,106 --> 00:08:29,701
(LAUGHING) Bobby. Hey. Hey,
no, I'm not ducking you.

160
00:08:29,776 --> 00:08:36,182
No. Hey, hey, yeah. Bobby,
yeah, I know what I said. Yeah.

161
00:08:36,249 --> 00:08:40,516
Yeah. Hey, look, Bobby, I can't give
you what I don't have. I'm tapped out.

162
00:08:40,587 --> 00:08:41,884
