the client's name.

209
00:10:34,567 --> 00:10:36,558
Oh, I... I'm...
I'm really sorry.

210
00:10:36,636 --> 00:10:38,001
(STUTTERING) I'm not
always like this.

211
00:10:38,071 --> 00:10:40,233
It's just that lately,
I've been...

212
00:10:40,306 --> 00:10:42,035
I'm Linda. Linda Gustavo.

213
00:10:42,108 --> 00:10:43,405
How do you do?

214
00:10:43,476 --> 00:10:46,104
Mrs. Hector Gustavo.

215
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:49,214
