You have to alienate people.

846
00:42:16,567 --> 00:42:17,728
You forced him
to lock you up.

847
00:42:17,802 --> 00:42:19,861
Oh, I didn't have to
force him very hard.

848
00:42:19,937 --> 00:42:22,065
Dennis, uh,
I need a favor.

849
00:42:22,140 --> 00:42:24,006
Yeah? So why are
you coming at me?

850
00:42:24,075 --> 00:42:25,099
You're my friend.

851
00:42:25,176 --> 00:42:27,736
You're not going to stop until
they cancel my pension, are you?

852
00:42:27,812 --> 00:42:30,144
Oh, Chapman knows
you're my friend.

853
00:42:30,248 --> 00:42:32,649
You're even officially
recognized by the IRS.

854
00:42:32,717 --> 00:42:35,914
